dc_description_s: This feature dataset includes the following feature classes: NRCS_SOIL, NRCS_SOIL_HYDRIC, NRCS_SOIL_HYDROLOGIC_GROUP, NRCS_SOIL_PI, NRCS_SOIL_PRIMEFARMLAND, NRCS_SOIL_PRIMEFARMLAND_ALLPRIME. It is a feature dataset within the geodatabase, NRCS_SOIL_021814_FGDB_v93.
